<task id="registering_walruses">
    <title>Register Walrus Pairs</title>
    <shortdesc/>
    <taskbody>
        <context>
        	<p>Because the CLCs communicate state automatically, you only need to register the redundant Walruses with one of the CLC components.</p>
        </context>
        <steps>
            <step>
            	<cmd>Log in to one of the CLC servers and enter the following command to register the
            		primary Walrus:</cmd>
            	<info>
            	<codeblock>/usr/sbin/euca_conf --register-walrus --partition=walrus --host=&lt;walrus_#1 IP_address> --component=walrus00</codeblock>
            	</info>
            </step>
        	<step>
        		<cmd>Enter the following command to register the secondary Walrus:</cmd>
        		<info>
        			<codeblock>/usr/sbin/euca_conf --register-walrus --partition=walrus --host=&lt;walrus_#2 IP_address> --component=walrus01</codeblock>
        		</info>
        	</step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task>
